# Stray Minecraft-format screenshots accidentally left in .modrinth/gallery/
# — gallery is manifest-driven (.modrinth/gallery.json), so files not in
# the manifest are ignored by the sync anyway; this just keeps `git status`
# clean.
.modrinth/gallery/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]_*.png
